# 7. 届いていたもの

Rin: <I don't know much about art...>
Rin: <I can't help you there... But seeing you tells me that what you're going through is a lot harder than I realize.>
Rin: <But this also isn't like you, Ena...>
Ena: What...?
Rin: <The Ena I know wouldn't be questioning whether or not you belong or whatever. She'd keep drawing no matter what.>
Ena: Oh...
Ena: Am I really that much of a musclehead...?
Ena: Still, you're right... I have to keep drawing if I wanna get better.
Len: <You have to keep drawing...>
Len: <Oh...>
Len: <Then, Ena... Um... Wanna try drawing us?>
Ena: Wait, you guys...?
Len: <Y-Yeah. Remember how you were able to figure out something when you drew Mafuyu that one time?>
Len: <So, I thought you drawing us might help you in the same way.>
Ena: Len...
Ena: Hehe. Thanks. Then, I'll try doing a quick sketch of you two.
Len: <Okay, great...!>
Ena: So, where should we do this? Would SEKAI be best if you two are gonna model for me?
Rin: <In that case, why don't we go over there...?>
Ena: Over where?
Len: <Oh, right... That could be really good practice for Ena...!>
Ena: Wait, where is this place you guys are talking about? I'm still totally in the dark.
Rin: <You'll know once you get here.>
Len: <We'll be waiting for you in SEKAI...!>
Ena: Whoa, what is this place...? Has it always been here?
Len: It's a new area that appeared the other day.
Rin: Yeah.
Rin: You said how you always have trouble drawing water that one time, so we thought it might be good practice.
Ena: Oh...
Ena: Now that you mention it, I did tell you guys that.
Ena: Then, I'll do my sketch here. I agree that it'll be good practice since it feels pretty strange and mysterious.
Ena: Would you guys mind placing yourselves a little closer to the water for me? Feel free to pose however you like.
Rin: How ever we like? That doesn't really help.
Ena: Hmm... Then, sit for me!
Len: O-Okay...!
Ena: (Still, this place is giving off some strange vibes...)
Ena: (I mean, it just appeared out of thin air?)
Ena: (At the same time...)
Ena: (A lot has been going through Mafuyu's mind after what happened with her mom...)
Ena: (This place appearing probably means she's feeling something different now.)
Len: Is something wrong, Ena...?
Ena: Nothing's wrong. More importantly, stay still!
Rin: It's your fault for keeping us waiting.
Ena: I'm drawing, I'm drawing.
Ena: Huh...?
Ena: Do you guys hear that...?
Len: Huh...?
Ena: Isn't this one of Kanade's songs...? It sounds like it's coming from the lake...
Len: Oh, right... That's been happening every now and again.
Ena: Wait, so it's really coming from within the lake? But why? How's that possible...?
Ena: Unless something's down there. Maybe a music player...?
Ena: Hang on...
Ena: Inside the lake—
Len: Ena, it isn't safe for you to walk in.
Ena: I know. But...
Ena: I could've sworn that I just saw one of my drawings down there just now.
Rin: One of your drawings...? I don't see anything.
Ena: It was only for a split second. It looked like...
Ena: I'm gonna see if I can...
Ena: Grab...it...
Ena: Nope. I can't seem to grab a hold of anything...
Ena: Hmm... I swear I saw it. Or it was just my imagination.
Rin: What was it a drawing of?
Ena: Huh? Uhh... It was my sketch of Mafuyu...
Len: Oh, the one you drew when she went over to stay at your house that one time?
Ena: Yeah, that's it. But there's no reason for it to be floating around inside this lake...
Rin: ...
Rin: What if it's because your sketch has some sort of special place in Mafuyu's heart?
Ena: What...?
Rin: This lake was born out of Mafuyu's feelings.
Rin: Seeing your sketch may've had some sort of effect on her. That might be why you're seeing it floating around now.
Ena: My sketch had an effect on her...?
Ena: This SEKAI really is strange.
Ena: (I was so sure that I had to keep getting better because I still didn't have what it takes. I thought I needed to give my future more thought...)
Ena: (But if my sketch managed to find a way into Mafuyu's heart...)
Ena: (If my art had a real effect on her...)
Ena: (Then, that means my art has the ability to reach others...)
Ena: (If that's true...)
Ena: Then, I need to keep improving little by little...
